summary: 1969  was a common year starting on Wednesday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: 1969  was a common year starting on Wednesday  of the Gregorian calendar, the 1969th year of the Common Era  and Anno Domini  designations, the 969th year of the 2nd millennium, the 69th year of the 20th century, and the 10th and last year of the 1960s decade. The year is associated with the first manned landing on the Moon .
